{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the biggest atrocities took place when they killed the Hungarian Jews in a matter of-- in a matter of six, seven weeks-- they killed close to half a million Jews in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyway, in Kosice-- in Slovakia, they opened the door and we had a chance to empty out the buckets, and to fill in some new water.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] they locked the doors again, and we started to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And again, all day, all night was going-- going until a day later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the first day [NON-ENGLISH]-- 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first day [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like 2 o'clock in the afternoon, and the train pulled in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I seen people when I looked through the little bit window I seen people dressed in stripe-- in stripe uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they opened up the doors and everybody said, [GERMAN], everybody get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told us to leave all the bundles on the-- on the-- on the-- what do you call it by the train there?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Platform.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the platform.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said, what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're going to get the bundles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now everybody got busy starting to write their names and addresses on the bundles, because if we are going to come back to pick up the bundles, we wanted to know which is our bundle.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody got busy with pens, with crayons, they started to write, to write, you know, the name, the address.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was busy writing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, you know, there were soldiers with dogs and they said, out, everybody, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they announced that all men, like from age 15 to 40, 45, I don't remember exactly, to stand on one side.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
